    <entry>
      <title>markdown语法</title>
      <link href="/2021/09/18/markdown%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95/"/>
      <url>/2021/09/18/markdown%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="笔记"><a href="#笔记" class="headerlink" title="笔记"></a><center>笔记</center></h1><h2 id="0-标题"><a href="#0-标题" class="headerlink" title="0.标题"></a>0.标题</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 一级标题</span><br><span class="line">……</span><br><span class="line">###### 六级标题</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="实例"><a href="#实例" class="headerlink" title="实例"></a>实例</h3><h1 id="这是一级标题"><a href="#这是一级标题" class="headerlink" title="这是一级标题"></a>这是一级标题</h1><h2 id="这是二级标题"><a href="#这是二级标题" class="headerlink" title="这是二级标题"></a>这是二级标题</h2><h6 id="这是六级标题"><a href="#这是六级标题" class="headerlink" title="这是六级标题"></a>这是六级标题</h6><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">别问三级到五级标题为什么不写</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="1-字体"><a href="#1-字体" class="headerlink" title="1.字体"></a>1.字体</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">*这是斜体*</span><br><span class="line">_这也是斜体_</span><br><span class="line">**这是粗体**</span><br><span class="line">__这也是粗体__</span><br><span class="line">***这是粗斜体***</span><br><span class="line">___这也是粗斜体___</span><br><span class="line">~~这是删除线~~</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="实例-1"><a href="#实例-1" class="headerlink" title="实例"></a>实例</h3><p><em>这是斜体</em><br><em>这也是斜体</em></p><hr><p><strong>这是粗体文本</strong><br><strong>这也是粗体</strong></p><hr><p><em><strong>这是粗斜体</strong></em><br><em><strong>这也是粗斜体</strong></em></p><hr><p><del>这是删除线</del></p><h2 id="2-列表"><a href="#2-列表" class="headerlink" title="2.列表"></a>2.列表</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">无序列表</span><br><span class="line">*</span><br><span class="line">+</span><br><span class="line">-</span><br><span class="line">有序列表</span><br><span class="line">1.</span><br><span class="line">……</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="实例-2"><a href="#实例-2" class="headerlink" title="实例"></a>实例</h3><h4 id="无序列表实例"><a href="#无序列表实例" class="headerlink" title="无序列表实例"></a>无序列表实例</h4><ul><li>这是一个无序列表</li></ul><ul><li>这是也一个无序列表</li></ul><ul><li>这是也一个无序列表<h4 id="有序列表实例"><a href="#有序列表实例" class="headerlink" title="有序列表实例"></a>有序列表实例</h4></li></ul><ol><li>这是一个有序列表</li><li>……<h2 id="3-引用"><a href="#3-引用" class="headerlink" title="3.引用"></a>3.引用</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&gt;内容</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="实例-3"><a href="#实例-3" class="headerlink" title="实例"></a>实例</h3><blockquote><p>引用内容</p></blockquote><h2 id="4-代码高亮"><a href="#4-代码高亮" class="headerlink" title="4.代码高亮"></a>4.代码高亮</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">`代码`</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="实例-4"><a href="#实例-4" class="headerlink" title="实例"></a>实例</h3><code>#include&lt;stdio.h&gt;</code><h2 id="5-链接"><a href="#5-链接" class="headerlink" title="5.链接"></a>5.链接</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[显示的内容](链接的地址)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="实例-5"><a href="#实例-5" class="headerlink" title="实例"></a>实例</h3><a href="https://caibing01.github.io/">本博客地址</a><h2 id="6-图片"><a href="#6-图片" class="headerlink" title="6.图片"></a>6.图片</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">![图片名](图片地址)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="实例-以本博客logo为例"><a href="#实例-以本博客logo为例" class="headerlink" title="实例(以本博客logo为例)"></a>实例(以本博客logo为例)</h3><img src="../../public/img/logo.png" alt="博客logo"><h2 id="7-表格-来源菜鸟教程"><a href="#7-表格-来源菜鸟教程" class="headerlink" title="7.表格(来源菜鸟教程)"></a>7.表格(来源菜鸟教程)</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">|  表头   | 表头  |</span><br><span class="line">|  ----  | ----  |</span><br><span class="line">| 单元格  | 单元格 |</span><br><span class="line">| 单元格  | 单元格 |</span><br><span class="line">-: 设置内容和标题栏居右对齐。</span><br><span class="line">:- 设置内容和标题栏居左对齐。</span><br><span class="line">:-: 设置内容和标题栏居中对齐</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="实例-6"><a href="#实例-6" class="headerlink" title="实例"></a>实例</h3><table><thead><tr><th align="left">左对齐</th><th align="right">右对齐</th><th align="center">居中对齐</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="left">单元格</td><td align="right">单元格</td><td align="center">单元格</td></tr><tr><td align="left">单元格</td><td align="right">单元格</td><td align="center">单元格</td></tr></tbody></table></li></ol><p><a href="https://www.runoob.com/markdown/md-table.html">菜鸟教程</a></p><h2 id="8-分割线"><a href="#8-分割线" class="headerlink" title="8.分割线"></a>8.分割线</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">***</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">___</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="实例-7"><a href="#实例-7" class="headerlink" title="实例"></a>实例</h3><hr><hr><hr><h2 id="9-支持html标签"><a href="#9-支持html标签" class="headerlink" title="9.支持html标签"></a>9.支持html标签</h2><h2 id="10-画流程图"><a href="#10-画流程图" class="headerlink" title="10.画流程图"></a>10.画流程图</h2><h2 id="11-公式"><a href="#11-公式" class="headerlink" title="11.公式"></a>11.公式</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$TeX 或 LaTeX 格式的数学公式$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="实例-无"><a href="#实例-无" class="headerlink" title="实例(无)"></a>实例(无)</h3><h2 id="12-转义"><a href="#12-转义" class="headerlink" title="12.转义"></a>12.转义</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">以反斜杆开头</span><br><span class="line">\   反斜线</span><br><span class="line">`   反引号</span><br><span class="line">*   星号</span><br><span class="line">_   下划线</span><br><span class="line">&#123;&#125;  花括号</span><br><span class="line">[]  方括号</span><br><span class="line">()  小括号</span><br><span class="line">#   井字号</span><br><span class="line">+   加号</span><br><span class="line">-   减号</span><br><span class="line">.   英文句点</span><br><span class="line">!   感叹号</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="第8-9-10-11-12点详情"><a href="#第8-9-10-11-12点详情" class="headerlink" title="第8,9,10,11,12点详情"></a>第8,9,10,11,12点详情</h4><p><a href="https://www.runoob.com/markdown/md-advance.html">点这里</a></p><h6 id="其中第7-11-12点可以使用工具”Typora”来实现"><a href="#其中第7-11-12点可以使用工具”Typora”来实现" class="headerlink" title="其中第7,11,12点可以使用工具”Typora”来实现"></a>其中第7,11,12点可以使用工具”Typora”来实现</h6><p><a href="https://typora.io/">官网地址</a></p><hr><hr><h1 id="以上内容仅为个人整理的笔记-方便以后查看"><a href="#以上内容仅为个人整理的笔记-方便以后查看" class="headerlink" title="以上内容仅为个人整理的笔记,方便以后查看"></a>以上内容仅为个人整理的笔记,方便以后查看</h1>]]></content>
      
      
